This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with finding correspondences in unorganized point clouds using a 3D local feature descriptor. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as point cloud processing is a common task in robotics. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning, which suggests it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with 3D representation and descriptor extraction, which could place it in the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
